{
  "name": "RPlog_Spa_Treatment",
  "title": "A Day at the Angry Rancor Spa",
  "summary": "At the luxurious spa aboard the Angry Rancor, the Nagai huntress Ash finally coaxes the battle-scarred Mandalorian Cantrell into a day of pampering, joining the regular patron Ka'una, a crimson Twi'lek, who is already soaking in the jacuzzi. The group trades banter about saunas, hunting expeditions, and the Pleasure Palace before moving on to deep-tissue massages that leave Cantrell groaning in unfamiliar bliss. They are joined by the cream-colored Twi'lek Nun'ia, the Rancor's cruise manager and an aspiring restaurateur, whose flirtations fluster the warrior even as her timidity around weapons draws gentle offers of self-defense training. Talk turns to Nun'ia's planned gladiatorial events, swordsmanship, and business dreams as the companions adjourn to the lounge, where Nun'ia serves a lavish meal she has cooked herself. Over steak, exotic ale, and dessert, the friends tease one another about etiquette, rations, and piercings, until Ash departs for a hunt and leaves Nun'ia alone with the Mandalorian she still finds quietly intimidating.",
